About this item

Product details

This Madden NYC Dome Backpack is the perfect carry-all to use when you need plenty of space! Ready to tackle your day, this backpack features seven spacious pockets to help keep your essentials sorted and easy to grab. Adorned with a laptop sleeve for those on-the-go workdays and a removable pouch that’s great for quick errands, makeup touch-ups, or keeping your phone close by. This dome backpack helps make getting organized stylish and cute.
  • Material: 100% Polyester
  • Care: Spot clean
  • Country of Origin: Imported
  • Exterior Dimensions: Approx. 18" H x 13" L x 6" W
  • Exterior Features: Detachable zippered pouch; padded; assorted colors or prints
  • Interior Features: Laptop sleeve; seven pockets
  • Handles: Adjustable shoulder straps
  • Weight: Approx. 41.6-oz.
